description: After missing her first flight and canceling, we gave her a second chance and she missed the flight again, then arrived 2 ½ hours late. After talking briefly she informed us she didn't know it was a hardcore bondage shoot. Hogtied is not for everybody and for this shoot we toned it down many levels. Before I stopped the shoot she did a great job. A note to future models, please take the time to find out what you're signing up for before you go to any shoot.
title: Morgan March
